rce/Ariadne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariadne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cousin\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe it was William Wordsworth who said, \\\"No matter what lies in front of you or behind you or to one side or the other, it matters more what comes from within\\\".\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wordsworth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.549232618474543e-42, \"text\": \"William Wordsworth\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wordsworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Wordsworth\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"one side\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matthew you are a \\\"champ\\\" too.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"champ\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks, mate!\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thanks, mate\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rod Stone, Greens Beach JUST watching a programme,Junior Doctors Down Under,where they are plonked into various ED on their first day.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greens_Beach,_Tasmania\", \"score\": 0.9999302479008126, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greens Beach\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greens_Beach,_Tasmania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greens_Beach,_Tasmania\"}, {\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4903824604298617e-12, \"text\": \"ED\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rod Stone\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"a programme\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"Junior Doctors\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"their first day\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh how I'd love to plonk our Premier, our Health Minister and our Treasurer into our EDs for the minimum of 10 weeks that these junior doctors have to work!\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our Premier\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"our Health Minister\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"our Treasurer\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"our EDs\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the minimum\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"10 weeks\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"these junior doctors\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wonder if the experience would give us more doctors and nurses and less stadium!\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"more doctors\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"nurses\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"less stadium\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not think the pollies would know what had hit them!\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pollies\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Glennis Sleurink, Launceston AUGUST 5-11 is Homelessness Week, a time to make louder our plea to our leaders to join us in taking urgent action to end homelessness.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Football_Club\", \"score\":